<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200929/85d70af7e91349a7ac4c2cd8c9db8333.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>华为哈勃投资光电转换器件研发商芯视界微电子，后者主营固态激光雷达芯片等</strong></p>
